org.firstinspires.ftc.teamcode.components.timers

Class IntervalTimer

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.firstinspires.ftc.teamcode.components.timers.IntervalTimer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IClock

    public class IntervalTimer
extends java.lang.Object
implements IClock
    The Interval Timer acts as a repeated timer that checks if the amount of time since the last time it was called exceeds the interval designated by the constructor.
